{"tid":285764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做左2星期gym 都未撚大隻","createTime":"2017-06-16T06:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T10:04:33.000Z","uid":14739,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26a9fa41b5b32f692cee76370b5e792c71f57272","tid":285764,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"明明一星期抽2日做<br />\n每個位做2set<br />\n但都未撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知gym room d 人係咪打針"},{"pid":"149c7c9cd7bc92fed861c51b2e3cd5de7c697ba1","tid":285764,"uid":43856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我尋日第一次做今日已經有腹肌啦"},{"pid":"c54f61a3e06b8c2dac5ddd5b514f30a2ee680a8e","tid":285764,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0cbd1cadf9317dba762da3b776dc79d0d41777f","tid":285764,"uid":58556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪姿勢唔岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身200幾磅肥仔黎<br />\n上次去gym room推左10下胸 跑左2km 就搞到好似美國隊長咁大隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebd571df7f07814df152b33507443bd80b4fdf4","tid":285764,"uid":30807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"注意下飲食啦，一味操得多冇用架<br />\n<br />\n平時淨食蛋白，一年操一次已經好fit"},{"pid":"62869e90784e8cfb9fb23dd82824a1ad061e99eb","tid":285764,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"你冇天份囉"},{"pid":"1b24f1bdf84de2c31c31ce7df722204ea8e545de","tid":285764,"uid":107042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"你悟性低"},{"pid":"8fd37a62da854e79a777e500cc63594b6a65843f","tid":285764,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4170a30ac3f6a6b7641c63e71b484ead5fceb601","tid":285764,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:34:14.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4ccabf0cc0355a3d377e7a077333cf93b31fd0","tid":285764,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:35:12.000Z","msg":"成班吹水怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我練左7年依家有麥浚龍身形，已經係 dream body都唔想練太大，有人想知點練再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbe4892ed2f57a0bb7eba9ad654111a876bf3fc","tid":285764,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"平時三個月操一次，每次做哂全身，各1set，做完隊返半打藍妹（大枝裝）；平時每星期至少8餐M記加大可樂走冰；呢加同雲迪素差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/143544_6adaeb122777e4aac491a844dfe7e227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F143544_6adaeb122777e4aac491a844dfe7e227.jpg&h=161328e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"312c0ff6201522ad1215ec946a7acc7e005198b1","tid":285764,"uid":82572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"一星期兩日梗係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肌肉都要休息，所以做一日就夠<br />\n每個位一set，做啱動作的話二星期就可以阿洛舒華咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要咪食粉，一食就好易變到太大隻"},{"pid":"32aa9e56fb06d12c0c948567ace2ee1794e0b828","tid":285764,"uid":93357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"每個位2set太多喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每個位1set就岩岩好"},{"pid":"7ed6b134f1510655ea85147f1d93749304a33f2a","tid":285764,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"俾啲掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee703a6dbe436125aaf08b1f7d3312b19068745","tid":285764,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"64c813c6a975a087397423612c47ab3dfc2fa933","tid":285764,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"做左半日都全身肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05460f5c2206886359a21f43914b5f9679e95c7c","tid":285764,"uid":12058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"係咪飲唔夠奶粉呀 我奶粉當水飲 做多下引體 第二日個背已經勁厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64fcab4068a93c2bd7c7ed41a6c33d6cd826f3c","tid":285764,"uid":10504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"淨係做幾下引體 <br />\n背肌已經好厚 <br />\n我怕再做落去 練到胡cfu咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a892ff8564a9069dac7603f85a83308269404b63","tid":285764,"uid":122931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"每個位一set 每組一下就夠啦<br />\n我驚你太大隻"},{"pid":"1d8288c67a6707c6fded19d926c8422009e74d73","tid":285764,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"講真 做兩之都未見效就唔好再晒時間操<br />\n因為你既基因入面已經決定左你有冇練肌肉既能力<br />\n如果冇既話你就算再努力都唔會有成果"},{"pid":"72200a1e50fbf84e0f6d1a4c2130932d103e9057","tid":285764,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"飲奶粉啦"},{"pid":"127504656c241f7141d63cf9646ab6757aec5d70","tid":285764,"uid":57367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"每日做10下掌上壓 一日5餐都係飲奶粉<br />\n一個月已經係張家輝身型"}]}